      <title>短期覆盖在最近的股票市场篮板之下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/short-covering-is-lying-beneath-the-recent-stock-market-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[S＆amp; p 500指数本周每天都开始对贸易战的担忧和经济增长放缓，只是为了恢复并陷入绿色。虽然股票市场的动作并不总是很清楚，但这些举动下的罪魁祸首是罪魁祸首：短期覆盖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/short-covering-is-lying-beneath-the-recent-stock-market-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 18:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨默斯说，特朗普征收施加油震类型经济命中率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/summers-says-trump-tariffs-to-impose-oil-shock-type-economic-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长劳伦斯·萨默斯（Lawrence Summers）表示，特朗普政府迫在眉睫的关税远足将对经济造成类似石油危机的震惊，从而缩小了其生产能力的能力＆mdash;提高价格和失业率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/summers-says-trump-tariffs-to-impose-oil-shock-type-economic-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 17:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
